description:
The playoff field is set after some exciting games on Sunday. The Washington Football Team (0:14) clinches the NFC East and a spot it the postseason with the win over the Eagles. Next up for Washington is a matchup with Tom Brady and the Bucs (0:59). The Browns making the playoffs for the first time in 18 years (2:18). They'll be joined by the Titans, Colts and Ravens as Lamar Jackson (3:35) makes NFL history
